::Ramulus::

Ramulus nods, rolling out of the way of some shots. "Let's go." he says.

Suddenly he crouches, turning his head toward the predacon base. Something 
was moving. Jumping around some trees, he nearly runs into Tarantulus.

"Put her down!" he says as fires a shot at the pred.
